## Data Attribution

Player statistics data is sourced from **FBref.com** (Sports Reference LLC).

- Website: https://fbref.com/
- All player data Â© Sports Reference LLC. All Rights Reserved.

This software is licensed under MIT, but the data itself is property of 
Sports Reference LLC and subject to their Terms of Service.

**Users of this software must:**
1. Provide clear attribution to FBref.com as the data source
2. Respect FBref's Terms of Service
3. Not use the data for commercial purposes without proper licensing from Sports Reference LLC
4. Include rate limiting in any scraping implementations (minimum 12 seconds between requests)

For questions about data licensing, contact Sports Reference LLC directly at https://fbref.com/
